{
  "title": "ISic000310. I.Sicily inscription 000310",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Timothy Smith; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Quintus\">Q(uintus)</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Lutatius\">Lutati[us</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">q</span>(uaestor) · d(ecreto) · d(ecurionum) aedil[is<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>pro hono[re<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ICHINOC̣ <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>I SVS Ị </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Timothy Smith; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Quintus\">Q</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Lutatius\">LUTATI[..</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Q</span>·D·DAEDIL[..<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>PROHONO[..<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ICHINO.<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ISVS.</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of CIL</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>Quintus Lutatius ..., quaestor by decree of the decurions, aedile ..., for the honour of...</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Manganaro (1989: 173) suggests possible restorations, which make this the granting of funds for funerary commemorations/banqueting: Q(uintus) Lutati[us - - -] q(uaestor) d(ecreto) d(ecurionum) aedil[is - - -] pro hono[re IIviratus tr]iclin[ium - - - cum] t[rib]us l[ectis dedit- - -]</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Carrera 1639 298 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002755\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002755</a>  </li><li> Mommsen 1883 <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">7026</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</a></li><li> Manganaro 1989 173 no.44 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
  "divs": [
    {
      "id": "editions",
      "html": "<div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Timothy Smith; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Quintus\">Q(uintus)</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Lutatius\">Lutati[us</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">q</span>(uaestor) · d(ecreto) · d(ecurionum) aedil[is<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>pro hono[re<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ICHINOC̣ <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>I SVS Ị </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Timothy Smith; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Quintus\">Q</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Lutatius\">LUTATI[..</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Q</span>·D·DAEDIL[..<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>PROHONO[..<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ICHINO.<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ISVS.</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div>"
